      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The action of the plumbers took the\ntrades council by storm last night\nwhen they formally announced that\nthey were on strike. Endorsement was\nnot granted until the next meeting. 1t\nIs customary for union when il con-\ntemplates a raise of wages to first\nrefer the matter to the main body\nthe trades council-and secure its en-\ndorsement. This, however, was not\ndone. but the plumbers struck of their\nown accord-and notified the council\natterward"
